{
  "stem": "21310.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was able to get in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "As I mentioned, I had a very good background.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I finished my lyceum in-- in the ghetto, actually.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I passed some exams.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I knew a teacher, a professor who was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he knew about the secret courses, the clandestine courses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I got in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I studied for-- for one year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean up till June.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then-- and the war ended in May.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then I learned that the United Nations are supporting some DP students in Germany, that they are planning or something to start to support them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so a group of us left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We went to Germany, illegally through really walking most, and with some horrid experiences with some Russians-- not actually Russians-- the Poles were worse.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "On the border, they were supposed to be bribed and let us through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So they robbed us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then when we were on top of a little bridge, they put all the floodlights on us, and they started shooting, but not really at us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But we didn't know, you see, so we had to run.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then we ran right into [LAUGHS] some Russians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And so it was quite-- you know, very-- a lot of experiences.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But finally, we went through the Russian zone, through the British zone, and finally I make my way to Wiesbaden.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then I-- I think it was Wiesbaden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Yeah, Wiesbaden.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then we were assigned to a university in Marburg, in Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we started to study medicine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Now, I already had two semesters behind me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So I was the more advanced of the group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We had a group of-- I forgot-- maybe 14 Jewish students.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But there were other DP students.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
